  <Cheat Text="[02][Special] LEON: 3 Stored Weapons Exchanged" Description="Three stored weapons will be exchanged, when you first open the storage case: Handcannon for Killer 7; Skull Shaker for Stingray; Chicago Sweeper for Rocket Launcher Infinite. In case you just wanted to exchange one or two of them, turn the cheat off, take the weapons you don't want to change, leave the storage/case, turn the cheat on and open the case again.">
